SOURCE: https://github.com/tinyplex/tinybase/blob/main/site/guides/05_synchronization/2_using_a_synchronizer.md#2025-04-16_snippet_7

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
import {createFilePersister} from 'tinybase/persisters/persister-file';

const persistingServer = createWsServer(
  new WebSocketServer({port: 8050}),
  (pathId) =>
    createFilePersister(
      createMergeableStore(),
      pathId.replace(/[^a-zA-Z0-9]/g, '-') + '.json',
    ),
);

persistingServer.destroy();
```

