TITLE: Creating a Hook for Managing Server Path IDs
DESCRIPTION: Implements a custom React hook that manages the unique path ID for collaborative spaces. It retrieves the ID from the URL query string and provides a function to generate new IDs.
SOURCE: https://github.com/tinyplex/tinybase/blob/main/site/demos/04_todo/v6.md#2025-04-16_snippet_7

LANGUAGE: js
CODE:
```
const useServerPathId = () => {
  const [serverPathId, setServerPathId] = useState(
    parent.location.search.substring(1),
  );
  return [
    serverPathId,
    useCallback(() => {
      const newServerPathId = getUniqueId();
      parent.history.replaceState(null, null, '?' + newServerPathId);
      setServerPathId(newServerPathId);
    }, []),
  ];
};
```

