TITLE: Implementing Checkpoints for Undo/Redo in TinyBase
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates how to implement undo/redo functionality using checkpoints in TinyBase.
SOURCE: https://github.com/tinyplex/tinybase/blob/main/site/home/index.md#2025-04-16_snippet_11

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
import {createCheckpoints} from 'tinybase';

const checkpoints = createCheckpoints(store);

store.setCell('pets', 'felix', 'sold', false);
checkpoints.addCheckpoint('pre-sale');

store.setCell('pets', 'felix', 'sold', true);
console.log(store.getCell('pets', 'felix', 'sold'));
// -> true

checkpoints.goBackward();
console.log(store.getCell('pets', 'felix', 'sold'));
// -> false
```

