TITLE: Function for Generating Ordinal Suffixes
DESCRIPTION: Utility function that adds the appropriate ordinal suffix (st, nd, rd, th) to the ranking number of a word.
SOURCE: https://github.com/tinyplex/tinybase/blob/main/site/demos/09_word_frequencies.md#2025-04-16_snippet_11

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
const suffix = (rank) => {
  switch (rank % 100) {
    case 11:
    case 12:
    case 13:
      return 'th';
  }
  switch (rank % 10) {
    case 1:
      return 'st';
    case 2:
      return 'nd';
    case 3:
      return 'rd';
    default:
      return 'th';
  }
};
```

