TITLE: Join Operation Example
DESCRIPTION: Shows how to join pet and owner tables using the ownerId as a foreign key.
SOURCE: https://github.com/tinyplex/tinybase/blob/main/site/guides/11_using_queries/2_tinyql.md#2025-04-16_snippet_4

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
